        packageId - id of package(-1 for one to be inserted)
        trackingNumber - tracking number of package
        receivedDate - Date package was scanned into system
        emailAddress - email address of recipient
        firstName - first name of recipient
        lastName - last name of recipient
        boxOffice - box/office number of recipient
        stop - Stop package to be delivered to
        courier - Courier who brought the package
        user - User who scanned it in
        atStop - wether package is at its stop waiting for pick up or not
        pickedUp - wether package has been received by recipient or not
        pickUpDate - Date package was picked up by recipient
        returned - wether package was returned
